Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.81,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.02,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!打倒杰克斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!杀死他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!莉莉娜殿下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的王兄!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光荣归于卫星!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.34,0:01:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七话\N背叛的遥远故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令部音讯全无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们逃出去!快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.89,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.69,0:01:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派遣宇宙军去卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,严厉限制卫星居民的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合高层崩溃后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙军也留在卫星\N巩固其支配权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在由西伯利亚升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的宇宙攻击用机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯的机动性面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的势力正不断减弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的士兵们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止无意义的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.94,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们OZ来宇宙是为了带来和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，一起迎接新时代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD部队没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说情况很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么\N叫无人陶拉斯回去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,护卫方面怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.21,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的人当机动战士是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日暂时让我独自行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部队解除战斗\N回去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD?无人战斗兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.34,0:03:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的OZ，开始了儿戏的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的居民应该是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.52,0:04:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N地球圈统一联合压制你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个联合的时代已经完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.73,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球，新的秩序将要建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个宇宙也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.03,0:04:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ会支持各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是OZ军\N不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是维持和平机关OZ送来的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我想讨论一下这议题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也不急于想要结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.99,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D区的卫星会议\N今日就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，别客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我现在以个人身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.54,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想所有卫星早晚会感谢OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个很年轻的领袖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能请你把年轻\N看做事一种可能性呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这种卫星第三世代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和不懂区别联合军与OZ的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也曾是隶属联合的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.63,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能马上要卫星的人了解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧联合的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还驻守在各处的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，我要解放下一个卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.44,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，还未请教芳名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.41,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是OZ在宇宙的指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令驻守在各卫星的\N旧联合军势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相继投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着OZ的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,设置在卫星间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙机雷的清除工程也开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，各卫星间的交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会再次开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ用什么手段也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不是要把卫星归其支配下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是最丑恶的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被武力强迫屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还会留有反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但若以支援的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星就会认同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为宇宙以轻率的家伙为主流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们毫无发觉OZ的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.84,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和钢弹一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.04,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹是为了卫星的人\N而造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能从OZ的阴谋里保护大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎样飞上宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们行动不能张扬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们反而要张扬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.99,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然OZ冒充和平企图支配卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们就不能再以卫星为挡箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ已经戴上虚假的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，卫星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就会知道OZ的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的OZ不会认为那是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.38,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我们又能战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回去宇宙吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令这一区的联合军全部投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是为暗杀希‧唯一事赎罪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用那样说吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说OZ和那件事有关的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终只是谣言!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是OZ说的不同版本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长老，你为何会来这里!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我听闻你们在商量认同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的OZ期望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不能轻易信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前和现在也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个蕾蒂‧安特校值得信任!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她以前多次采用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血腥的高压行动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是谣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她现在不是正亲自指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清除宇宙机雷\N这种危险任务吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他们想得到宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们现在为卫星工作是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ想向我们伸出和平之手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不应该拒绝他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球友好是我们的基本政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.69,0:08:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们认同OZ吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只是一群可恶的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在叫MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去宇宙机雷区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙机雷接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是尼高尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,P0314区工程完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.52,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扫宇宙也变得简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在卫星D13087
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现疑似钢弹制造工场的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及逮捕了一名技术师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上回来司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个男人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指挥官终于出场了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军部机械工场的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有能制造机动战士的外部区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他把那里破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毁灭证据吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.23,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜，他也毁灭了资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你造出钢弹的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人这样发问的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该和那5部钢弹有关!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和其余4部无关呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我造出最好的钢弹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何须要造出4部不同的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说你造出的只有1部吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是名为[死神钢弹]的杰作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星间的往来和通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直被联合封锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是造了1部出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧合?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说有5部是巧合吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校!地球有通讯来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新加坡宇宙港基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正受到钢弹02和04的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然要回来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ的大型基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样不能前进啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要一口气冲去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士升空用的HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔!别勉强!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉强也好，我要大家知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要战斗到同伴知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要大家看见我们的战斗后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道须要回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙在等我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和大家一起去宇宙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们正攻击OZ在地球的基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合军的确会迫害卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而OZ也会隶属联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何一个卫星向地球投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也并非不能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在正是要OZ重新知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们对和平的渴求的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可以永远拿着武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.00,0:12:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们相信战斗有助于保护卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!现在对卫星来说是麻烦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在OZ不信任我们之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该表明自己的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.78,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为爱\N因为此任何人更爱卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们选择了战斗之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹…在拼死战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们…以些微的力量在反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.83,0:13:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们为何不保护那些钢弹!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.52,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我们的事全世界都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要发表宇宙卫星D区的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为钢弹的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正进行破坏OZ的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们D区和钢弹毫无关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们宣布若钢弹当OZ是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我们也就成为钢弹的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ光明正大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相的误解已经消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在希望钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.72,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这场战斗里被击倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们希望所有区域的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会认同这宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.19,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白!我明白但受不了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们本来就是独自来到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在得不到卫星明白也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有和我一条心并肩作战的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.12,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起来!沙漠钢弹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不可以被击倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去会没命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该在做正确的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何要死在这种地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为我们是正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是正义!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.65,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正义的人不强大怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你们到此为止没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.05,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后的就留给剩下的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我把之后的交给你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若死在这里，你们会对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.67,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得赞同你们所想的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家注意到了吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…大家知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的任务是消灭OZ组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果OZ上了宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要追上去消灭他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗会变得艰辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.71,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我从五颗心里感到详和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五名技术者躲藏的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然其他四名轻易被逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.49,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但始终也会有人顽强反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校\N虽然卫星外围区域有工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但通往内部的通路完全被封闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发出劝降警告了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告被忽视了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不用客气，开始攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!卫星有热源反应!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体散开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两部有人机被毁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部队\N因反应速度快没损毁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD部队专用雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!雷射炮太强了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.34,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接击中卫星\N会有很严重的损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.31,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的战斗方式何时起变得有礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥尔，我现在并非进行外交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该正在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星并非被我们的攻击毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.26,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是被叛乱份子所毁灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的精神仍然卑鄙无耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我就自动投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我接受你的投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的人早晚也会发觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.98,0:18:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ邪恶的一面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会白费这些孩子的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点!卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体包围钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有机动战士升空用HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去，升空时会被围攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔!快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管我，我决定了要掩护升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定要去宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.72,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，所以我在这里掩护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少你们两个能去到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.59,0:19:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.76,0:19:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你!\N动作快点，我快支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我去宇宙就是向你报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,余下…余下的武器…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自爆装置呢
